  {
    "hotel_id": "5928553",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/oriental-hotel-fukuoka-hakata-station/hotel/fukuoka-jp.html",
    "name": "ORIENTAL HOTEL FUKUOKA HAKATA STATION",
    "detail": "This hotel apparently recently re-opened after refurbishment (April 2019), so interior and furnishings are nice and new. It's location is really very convenient - a stone's throw away from Hakata train station, which is a main transit hub for other places in Fukuoka, so has plenty of places to eat, shop, etc. whether you are staying or en route elsewhere. We enjoyed the very easy access to the station malls and restaurants, major tourist attractions in the city, as well as the airport (bus stop nearby and train, accessible from the hotel basement entrance). Staff were extremely courteous and friendly, and offered thoughtful touches at the hotel, such as personalised mini-guides to the best ramen in town, as well as a matcha tea ceremony (free for guests on selected days of the week). We enjoyed our stay there. Thank you, Oriental Hakata Hotel Fukuoka Station team! ",
